*Galax urceolata* (Poiret) Brummitt

dominated by red maple and chestnut oak, often near
*Rhododendron maximum*. Moderate S-facing slope on Big
Ridge, a spur off Pine Mountain. Off St. Rt. 630 NE of
Hwy 23 and ca. 4.5 km NNE of Pound, Va. El. ca.
2100ft.
